TEST_TYPE: Integration
PRECONDITIONS: >>>
- <Module A> and <Module B> are integrated and initialised.
- System is in normal operating state.
<<<
STEPS: >>>
1. Set <DataItem_1> = <value outside valid range, e.g. max + 1>.
2. Trigger one execution cycle of <Module A>.
3. Read return code and fault log from <Module B>.
4. Read system state after one additional execution cycle.
<<<
