[REQUIREMENT]
UID: SAD-091
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Verification records and verdict
STATEMENT: >>>
The Software Architecture and Design Verification Report shall include:

  - Date and revision of each design deliverable reviewed.
  - Name, role, and independence evidence of the verifier.
  - Checklist results: each item marked Pass / Fail / N/A with observations.
  - List of findings: unique identifier, description, severity
    (Critical / Major / Minor / Observation), and status.
  - Action items raised, with reference to the action item register.
  - Resolution evidence for all Critical and Major findings.
  - Overall verdict: Approved / Approved with conditions / Not approved.

Architecture and design documents shall not be baselined and the software
implementation phase (EN 50716:2023, Clause 7.4) shall not commence until
an Approved verdict is recorded.

Verification Report reference: <document ID>
Verdict: <to be completed upon review>
Date of approval: <YYYY-MM-DD>
